<p><cite id="endnote_Mengernone"><a href="#ref_Mengernone" title=""><b><sup>^</sup></b></a></cite>&#160;<cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFMenger1934"><a href="/wiki/Karl_Menger" title="Karl Menger">Menger, Karl</a> (August 1934). "Das Unsicherheitsmoment in der Wertlehre Betrachtungen im Anschlu√ü an das sogenannte Petersburger Spiel". <i>Zeitschrift f√ºr National√∂konomie</i> <b>5</b> (4): 459‚Äì485. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1007%2FBF01311578" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1007%2FBF01311578" rel="nofollow">10.1007/BF01311578</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a> <a href="http://www.worldcat.org/issn/0931-8658" class="external text" title="http://www.worldcat.org/issn/0931-8658" rel="nofollow">0931-8658</a> (Paper) <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a> <a href="http://www.worldcat.org/issn/1617-7134" class="external text" title="http://www.worldcat.org/issn/1617-7134" rel="nofollow">1617-7134</a> (Online).</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Das+Unsicherheitsmoment+in+der+Wertlehre+Betrachtungen+im+Anschlu%C3%9F+an+das+sogenannte+Petersburger+Spiel&amp;rft.jtitle=Zeitschrift+f%C3%BCr+National%C3%B6konomie&amp;rft.aulast=Menger&amp;rft.aufirst=Karl&amp;rft.au=Menger%2C+Karl&amp;rft.date=August+1934&amp;rft.volume=5&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=459%E2%80%93485&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1007%2FBF01311578&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:St._Petersburg_paradox"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></p>
<p><cite id="endnote_Riegernone"><a href="#ref_Riegernone" title=""><b><sup>^</sup></b></a></cite>&#160;<cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFRiegerMei_Wang2006">Rieger, Marc Oliver; Mei Wang (August 2006). "Cumulative prospect theory and the St. Petersburg paradox". <i>Economic Theory</i> <b>28</b> (3): 665‚Äì679. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1007%2Fs00199-005-0641-6" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1007%2Fs00199-005-0641-6" rel="nofollow">10.1007/s00199-005-0641-6</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a> <a href="http://www.worldcat.org/issn/0938-2259" class="external text" title="http://www.worldcat.org/issn/0938-2259" rel="nofollow">0938-2259</a> (Paper) <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a> <a href="http://www.worldcat.org/issn/1432-0479" class="external text" title="http://www.worldcat.org/issn/1432-0479" rel="nofollow">1432-0479</a> (Online).</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Cumulative+prospect+theory+and+the+St.+Petersburg+paradox&amp;rft.jtitle=Economic+Theory&amp;rft.aulast=Rieger&amp;rft.aufirst=Marc+Oliver&amp;rft.au=Rieger%2C+Marc+Oliver&amp;rft.au=Mei+Wang&amp;rft.date=August+2006&amp;rft.volume=28&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=665%E2%80%93679&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1007%2Fs00199-005-0641-6&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:St._Petersburg_paradox"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> (<a href="http://www.sfb504.uni-mannheim.de/publications/dp04-28.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.sfb504.uni-mannheim.de/publications/dp04-28.pdf" rel="nofollow">Publicly accessible, older version.</a>)</p>
<p><cite id="endnote_Samuelsonnone"><a href="#ref_Samuelsonnone" title=""><b><sup>^</sup></b></a></cite>&#160;<cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFSamuelson1960">Samuelson, Paul (January 1960). "The St. Petersburg Paradox as a Divergent Double Limit". <i>International Economic Review</i> <b>1</b> (1): 31‚Äì37. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F2525406" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F2525406" rel="nofollow">10.2307/2525406</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+St.+Petersburg+Paradox+as+a+Divergent+Double+Limit&amp;rft.jtitle=International+Economic+Review&amp;rft.aulast=Samuelson&amp;rft.aufirst=Paul&amp;rft.au=Samuelson%2C+Paul&amp;rft.date=January+1960&amp;rft.volume=1&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=31%E2%80%9337&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.2307%2F2525406&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:St._Petersburg_paradox"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></p>
